-700 dark:text-ink-200">Investigation record of what happened</label><div class="mt-1.5"><textarea rows="4" placeholder="" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm"></textarea></div></div><div class="md:col-span-12"><label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-ink-200">Investigation finding</label><div class="mt-1.5"><textarea rows="4" placeholder="" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm"></textarea></div></div><div class="md:col-span-12"><label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-ink-200">Outcome/action following — mitigate further incidents</label><div class="mt-1.5"><textarea rows="4" placeholder="" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm"></textarea></div></div><div class="md:col-span-6"><label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-ink-200">Investigation action completed?</label><div class="mt-1.5"><select class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 bg-white dark:bg-ink-900 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm"><option>Yes</option><option>No</option></select></div></div><div class="md:col-span-6"><label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-ink-200">Investigation action date completed</label><div class="mt-1.5"><input type="date" placeholder="" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm" /></div></div><div class="md:col-span-12"><label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-ink-200">Participant / representative feedback / comments</label><div class="mt-1.5"><textarea rows="4" placeholder="" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm"></textarea></div></div><div class="md:col-span-6"><label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-ink-200">Is this a reportable incident?</label><div class="mt-1.5"><select class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 bg-white dark:bg-ink-900 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm"><option>Yes</option><option>No</option></select></div></div><div class="md:col-span-6"><label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-ink-200">Signature of Line Manager</label><div class="mt-1.5"><input type="text" placeholder="" class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-ink-800 focus:border-brand-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-100 outline-none text-sm" /></div></div></div>
</section>
